                <strong>The EEP Team</strong>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need assistance? Contact us:</p>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <a href="mailto:info@hitoai.ai">Email Us</a>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/hitoai-limited/" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
            </div>
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> HitoAI Limited. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>